{{字节单位}}
-{zh-cn:'''泽[[字节|字节]]'''或'''泽它字节'''; zh-tw:'''皆[[位元組|位元組]]''';}-（{{lang-en|Zettabyte}}，縮寫為'''ZB'''）是一種資訊計量[[单位_(度量衡)|單位]]，通常在標示網路硬碟總容量，或具有大容量的儲存媒介時使用。

== 與其他儲存單位的換算 ==
*1ZB = 1,000 [[EB|EB]] 
*1ZB = 1,000,000 (10<sup>6</sup>)[[拍字节|PB]]
*1ZB = 1,000,000,000 (10<sup>9</sup>)[[太字节|TB]]
*1ZB = 1,000,000,000,000 (10<sup>12</sup>)[[GB|GB]]
*1ZB = 1,000,000,000,000,000 (10<sup>15</sup>)[[百萬位元組|MB]]
*1ZB = 1,000,000,000,000,000,000 (10<sup>18</sup>)[[千字节|KB]]
*1ZB = 1,000,000,000,000,000,000,000 (10<sup>21</sup>)[[位元組|B]]

另外，Zettabyte往往亦可以指[[Zebibyte|Zebibyte]]，其换算公式是：
*1ZiB = 1,024 [[Exbibyte|EiB]] 
*1ZiB = 1,048,576 (1024<sup>2</sup>)[[Pebibyte|PiB]] 
*1ZiB = 1,073,741,824 (1024<sup>3</sup>)[[Tebibyte|TiB]] 
*1ZiB = 1,099,511,627,776 (1024<sup>4</sup>)[[Gibibyte|GiB]]
*1ZiB = 1,125,899,906,842,624 (1024<sup>5</sup>)[[Mebibyte|MiB]]
*1ZiB = 1,152,921,504,606,846,976 (1024<sup>6</sup>)[[Kibibyte|KiB]]
*1ZiB = 1,180,591,620,717,411,303,424 (1024<sup>7</sup>)[[Byte|B]]

